9 An Act relating to criminal case fees; amending 28
O.S. 2021, Section 153, as last amended by Section 5,
10 Chapter 305, O.S.L. 2025 (28 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
153), which relates to costs in criminal cases;
11 requiring the collection of costs from defendants
convicted of certain criminal offenses; and providing
12 an effective date.
